Class SizeValidator<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gwtbootstrap3.client.ui.form.validator.AbstractValidator<T>
      • org.gwtbootstrap3.client.ui.form.validator.SizeValidator<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the generic type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Validator<T>

    public class SizeValidator<T>
extends AbstractValidator<T>
    Validator for checking the length of a map, array, collection, or string value. If type is not one of the aformentioned, the Object.toString() method is called to get the string representation of the object.
    Author:
    Steven Jardine
